Property Description: Ready to move, this spacious 3BHK GDA Approved builder floor is stretched across an area of 150 sqyrd and is up for sale in Avantika Colony, Ghaziabad. Please take a note this is not unapproved freehold construction, its a GDA Approved Property with loan easily available. It has 2 master bedrooms with size 13 x 12 and one 10x10, one store attached with master bedroom and one bathroom attached with other master bedroom.  It has hall with approx 10 x 26 with one bathroom attached to it. One bathroom is indian style and other is western style.  It is 3 years old property and it has a bank load on rs. 18 lakhs from PNB which can be transferred of paid at the time of deal.  Property specifications: Worth living, this 3BHK flat is facing south direction and is comparatively a new property with age of construction being less than 5 years. Moreover, it is positioned on the advantageous ground floor in a building of three floors. The entire flat is decked with Vitrified flooring that lends an attractive look to this abode. This flat consists of three bedrooms, dining cum living room, kitchen, two bathrooms and a store room. All the bedrooms are elegantly designed and one of the bedrooms is furnished with wardrobes. The kitchen is set up with stainless steel sink, cabinets and chimney, thereby making it convenient for cooking. Of the two bathrooms, one is common that is Indian style while the other western style bathroom is attached cum common with interconnecting doors. Also, provision for geyser is available in all the bathrooms. Furthermore, one sit out is available at the entry while the other is common between two bedrooms covered with grilled iron roof. Additionally, there is a store room attached to the bedroom. Facilities Covered parking facility is allotted for one car to park. To look after the repair issues of the occupants, there are plumbers and electricians readily accessible.   Locality: Located in a prime residential area of Ghaziabad, this flat is well connected to all the essential facilities. Chiranjiv Plaza, local market and daily needs shops are accessible within 500meter radius from this area. Gurukul The School, Nehru World School and Ryan International School are reachable within 1.5-2.5 km radius. Columbia Asia Hospital - Ghaziabad and Prime Hospital are few medical aids accessible within 2-4 km from this property. Conveyance is easy as there is local bus stop within 200 meters and various means of public transport are in proximity. You can find Syndicate Bank, ICICI Bank within 1.5 km while IDBI, AXIS, PNB, SBI, ICICI ATMs are reachable within 500 meter from this property.
